Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:54.96,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:09.43,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,It's fall now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:18.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0025,,Huh?  So then your father was a tank rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:19.46,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0025,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:21.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0025,,He was one of the legendary heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:24.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,,0000,0000,0025,,who freed over a thousand civilians and soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:27.44,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0025,,from the completely-encircled Waldenborough.{is there a place name we can reference?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:31.60,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0025,,And with only six Milivets{? names suck}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.15,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0025,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:35.32,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:39.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,And also, when my father was honorably wounded in the midst of battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:43.10,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,he was sent to the hospital where my mother was working as an orderly, and that's how they met! {sakusen chuu ni meiyo no fushou wo otta tousan ha nyuuinsaki de eiseihei datta kaasan wo deau no yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:46.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,And then from the two of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:48.48,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,you were born, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:49.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:54.05,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you comparing me to a potato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:57.20,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.  What a fine-looking potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:00.13,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to your earnest and diligent care of them, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:06.85,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,With this, it looks like we'll be able to share some with the citizens, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:09.91,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,And Krause-san is coming, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.62,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we take some as a present for him, also?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:18.27,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan, you really like Krause-san, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:22.39,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not about like, it's about respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.43,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Poke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,{wth...so weird.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:45.22,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:49.46,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so she's able to play songs like that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.46,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:52.79,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:03.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,The wind's picked up, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.65,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,The weather doesn't look like it's going to hold up for much longer, either.  Shall we head inside before that happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:10.48,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.31,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.46,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-chan, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:13.11,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:24.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:29.09,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Like I was saying, don't you think something's up with Rio-sempai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:30.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:32.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Like her trumpet-playing and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.49,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,It's just wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.32,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds so cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,She's seems to be kind of depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:39.70,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,It's normal for her not to waste words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.05,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.30,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!  Dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Was delicious, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:44.73,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Tempura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:47.28,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!  And the potatoes were so crispy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:48.72,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{man. they should just talk like this all the time. teenagers/hs convos are so much easier to tl}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:56.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Rio.  Eat it while it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:03.88,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:04.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Past,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Good, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:13.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,She was scarfing down those green peppers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:15.44,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Rio-senpai was?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:23.40,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!  The same Rio-senpai who, no matter how finely chopped up they are, {\i1}always{\i0} finds and takes them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:26.50,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,That... could be a bad sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.40,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Poke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:41.89,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.66,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... Krause-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.36,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!  That's my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:53.38,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,The Desert Wolf, Miracle Krause!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:59.97,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,On his left pec{am i using the right word? she says chest, but we don't have left chests -_-} is a wolf-head tattoo that represents the unity and glory of the 481st Platoon! {shoutai no kessoku to eikou shimesu wolf head tattoo}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.29,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:03.71,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.72,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you need to worry too much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:14.43,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the whole thing with the captain was because we worried too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:20.67,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,And this time, it's {\i1}Rio-senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:23.36,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cool and awesome and sexy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:24.48,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:29.78,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she's even gotten over her dislike of green peppers and is able to eat them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:33.79,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan, you really like Rio-senpai, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:36.85,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,She's my idol after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:39.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she's mine too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:41.34,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think, Noel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,P... oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:50.77,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful! {that's dangerous!}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,{this show. what. ewwwww}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:03.66,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-chan's already out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no helping that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,She can share my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.69,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, you get that end?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:32.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot to turn off the heating fire for the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:34.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I completely forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:40.05,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,How you seem so focused and steady, yet sometimes slip up, is one of your charming points. {kimeteruyou de doko ka de nuketeru no ga}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:42.67,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, it's been happening too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.16,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:50.06,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret it?  Hanging up on your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:56.43,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess there's nothing to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:59.95,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover for your mistakes at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:07.66,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,But at least stay a cool senpai around those children, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.19,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that's the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:17.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:19.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for coming by so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Class-1 Priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Who's it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:27.49,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Major Kazumiya Rio of the 1121st Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.11,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:43.55,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Major, for the moment, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:46.61,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,You can't possibly travel anymore in this weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:48.47,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are the Desert Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:52.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you not to call me that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:52.97,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:57.50,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,To make up for it, how about a bath and some hot tea? {WINK xD; LOOOOOOOL ~Sumi}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:05.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for completing your mission in this typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:11.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Um, sorry that all we have to offer you are leftovers from dinner... but please, partake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:18.79,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,You should've woken me up when Krause-san got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:25.24,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:28.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Despite the fact they're cold.  Even the green peppers are good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:30.10,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:33.26,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who picked them and fried them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:37.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be a great wife one day, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.63,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the new paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:44.34,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the Major brought it here for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:46.30,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,How are the armistice arrangements going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:49.89,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,The conference still appears to be going through some rough patches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:51.93,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like neither side is willing to compromise on their conditions...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:57.33,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,If only Princess Ilya were still alive, those talks might be going differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.61,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Princess... Ilya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:05.86,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really not know who that is?!  The hero of Vingt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:09.54,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,The first princess of His Royal{i'm assuming gender, japanese never has gender >< his highness can also be taken out if you'd like} Highness, the Archduke Arcadia! {arcadia taikou denka no dai ichi koujyou datta kata yo} {http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Style_%28manner_of_address%29 & more specifically http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imperial_and_Royal_Highness for your perusal, mid ~Sumi}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.37,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,The goddess of victory for the Helvetian army!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:16.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,A tank rider goddess, right up there with Desert Wolf Krause!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha, that's actually—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:23.31,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,There's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:39.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.19,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,{open ittttttt x.x}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.87,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:56.86,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,One of the kids from Yumina's place has been missing since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:58.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Will you help us search for him? {gender not yet mentioned}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:58.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:01.11,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san, who's missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.85,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,It's Seiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.54,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0025,,The river's swelled quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:24.03,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0025,,I'm sure the fields downstream haven't been harvested yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:26.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0025,,If the dam breaks, they'll be completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:29.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0025,,I'm unfamiliar with the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:30.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0025,,I'm counting on you, Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:31.92,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0025,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.03,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.91,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Yumina,0000,0000,0025,,I only took my eyes off of him for a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:42.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0025,,Disaster relief also falls under military duties.  Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:50.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:50.93,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.15,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:53.19,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.16,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:55.93,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:57.31,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:58.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:10.45,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... the water's risen this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.45,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,If he fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:21.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.98,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What was that? {man. he sounds really old all of a sudden}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:30.77,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:35.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,You know something, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.72,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,You have a lead, that's why you came out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.14,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:42.53,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Seiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,At the fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:48.53,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,"The fields"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:51.80,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,Eggplants are Yumina-oneechan's favorite food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:56.77,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,So we used all of everyone's allowances and bought seeds...{http://jisho.org/words?jap=%E8%8B%97&eng=&dict=edict idk i don't think eggplants have seedlings. i think only trees do and eggplants are on vines, no? so maybe just seeds}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:58.28,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Mishio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Seiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:02.14,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.30,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:31.54,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Coming to a place like this in the middle of a typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.14,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna protect the eggplants!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:35.67,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!  You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.71,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's risking their lives for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.61,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,I never asked you to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:41.08,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,You came here on your own! {these two lines are flipped, but it makes more sense to say them in this order in english}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:43.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better cut that out—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:53.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:56.89,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Kids without parents need to be stronger than those with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:14:00.74,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,When you cause trouble for others, they'll naturally say that's to be expected from someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,And they won't say it just to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:08.74,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,They'll say it to others too, like your sis, Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.41,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha... {So... we're just ditching the rope-holding, I guess....? ~Sumi}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:17.53,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,I know because I'm an orphan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:21.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:22.73,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.13,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still complaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.61,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:34.21,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Something you've worked for and raised can have as much value as your own life, you know? {tansei shite sodateta montte no ha inochi to onaji gurai kawaii mon da yo na}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:40.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,These have grown large enough to be eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:44.82,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,If you turn them into pickled vegetables{http://jisho.org/words?jap=tsukemono&eng=&dict=edict}, they'll be delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.07,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Seiya,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.07,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Major...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:04.49,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-kun's started climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:17.78,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Major, please, you go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:18.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:27.47,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... you go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.93,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:31.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,{AHHHHH she's - she's omg SO GONNA FALL}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,{or no. we'll just have cute moments xD}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:01.61,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, they're both still safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:02.78,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.45,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Now their way back up is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:10.19,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,This is... a terrible situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:19.36,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:20.54,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...{if you deem a line necessary. otherwise, just don't put anything}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.72,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,The situation's taken a turn for the worse, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:26.21,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,But {\i1}you{\i0} are with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.62,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure things will work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.51,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.58,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.81,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.67,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!  Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:48.61,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,You're with Miracle Krause now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.74,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.60,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,The ground won't hold much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:54.65,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Another disaster, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:58.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!  This is why I hate kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:03.32,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Kids who don't listen should just be tied up and locked away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:04.12,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.13,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,What will saying that to them do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:11.82,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids are always looking up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:16.37,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... that was too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:20.13,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I'm sure that things will be okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.84,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Krause-san is called a miracle person and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.03,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:30.19,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,He's not the Desert Wolf or Miracle Krause.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:35.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,He just coincidentally happens to have the same name and a similar appearance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:40.01,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,When they first met, Kureha just started calling him that on her own and got all excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:42.65,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,And Krause isn't much of a talker, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:46.02,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,He never found the right time to deny her misconceptions and time went on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:48.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:53.46,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, now we need to think of a way to save the two of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:56.87,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The one only a courier, but with many years of continuous service,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:59.77,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,and the other with a lot of enthusiasm, but no experience. {tonikaku ima ha kinzoku ni suu ga nagai dake no ichi tsushinhei to yaruki ha aru ga keiken ha kakenu? mono futari gumi wo asoko kara tsukuidasu houhou wo kagaerunda}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:02.43,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hand them... a rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:05.20,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,There's no firm footing above them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:09.17,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,And it's too far to send them one from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:13.65,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,To get a rope from here over to there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:15.68,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,There's a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.78,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met you, Krause-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:25.16,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, if my father were still alive, I'm sure he would be just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:31.71,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,I speak to everyone as if I knew my father really well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:37.55,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,But well, it's really all just passed-down information and I don't actually know who he was that well at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:41.48,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I was old enough to know what was going on, he was already gone. {http://jisho.org/words?jap=monogokoro&eng=&dict=edict my wording might not be best - this is referring to about...4 or 5 years old? very young.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:42.48,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:10.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention to... the upper-left?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:19.26,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!  Heave-ho!  Heave-ho!  Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:14.25,SoRaNoWoTo-Alt,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}Takemikazuchi{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:20.33,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.75,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-chan, how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:29.23,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Anchoring linear coil ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:33.61,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Targeting systems B7 to F5 partially active.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.64,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Initiating alignment. {targeting}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:43.15,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.16,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire the wire anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:47.66,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:48.69,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:19:59.91,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:06.39,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,In place of your late father, I will protect you! {he doesn't say promise.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.94,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.44,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:16.44,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylica,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:27.65,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:28.44,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.00,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.96,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Pull up the anchor!  Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.95,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:14.95,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Things worked out somehow, so I'm going to go ahead and say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:15.92,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.83,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,You really are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.42,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kureha,0000,0000,0000,,someone I admire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:38.49,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,A blue sky after the typhoon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:40.69,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,You kept it up til the end, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:44.90,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Rio,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I'm surprised.  I wasn't sure you had it in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:48.11,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw those eyes that watched me with such complete faith,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:52.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,I became more afraid of destroying her dreams than of dying.{should I split this? maybe editing to make it shorter will be better -yuuri}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:56.29,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was able to play it out til the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:22:01.04,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm a coward, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:02.58,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:04.32,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,Krause-san, you were wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:07.47,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Listen here, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:12.06,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the time, what you see when observing someone from the outside
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.72,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,and what the person is feeling inside are different. {hata kara mieru mon to touno honnin ga kanjiteru mon ha taitei no baai chigatterun da}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:19.35,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Watching someone through lenses of admiration always makes your vision out of focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:25.07,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, when you're looked at through such lenses, you'll understand how hard it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:29.11,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Phylicia,0000,0000,0000,,Could you at least stay until Kureha-chan wakes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:31.99,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell her for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:38.33,SoRaNoWoTo-Main,Krause,0000,0000,0000,,That this is the most honorable wound I've received in my entire life!
